Jason GREER, petitioner,
v.
UNITED STATES.
No. 17-8775.
Supreme Court of the United States
Oct. 15, 2018.
Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Tenth Circuit denied.
Justice SOTOMAYOR, dissenting from the denial of certiorari: I dissent from the denial of certiorari for the reasons set out in Brown v. United States , 586 U.S. ----, 139 S.Ct. 14, --- L.E.2d ---- (2018) ( Sotomayor, J., dissenting). Justice GORSUCH took no part in the consideration or decision of this petition.
